
Overview of adj pitiless

The adj pitiless has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (2) pitiless, remorseless, ruthless, unpitying -- (without mercy or pity; "an act of ruthless ferocity"; "a monster of remorseless cruelty")
2. pitiless, unkind -- (deficient in humane and kindly feelings)
